		<h2 class="story">
				
				
				
			<span id="title-21538756"> <a   href="//it.slashdot.org/story/11/06/10/0741204/explaining-the-business-of-spam">Explaining The Business of Spam</a></span>
			
			
			<span class="comments commentcnt-21538756" >74</span>
			

                        
		</h2>
		<div class="details" id="details-21538756">
		
		Posted
		by 
	
	
		
			<a href="http://www.monkey.org/~timothy/" rel="nofollow">timothy</a>
		
	
	

	
	
	<time id="fhtime-21538756" datetime="on Friday June 10, 2011 @06:20AM">on Friday June 10, 2011 @06:20AM</time>
	
	
		<br>from the wading-through-the-muck-even-now dept.
	
